; Coverage for history.cc: multi-step price conversion via dijkstra path
; Exercises find_price with source+target, path traversal, last_target assignment
; A->B->C chain: 10 A * 2 B/A * 3 C/B = 60 C

P 2024/01/01 A 2 B
P 2024/01/01 B 3 C

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses:Test    10 A
    Assets:Cash

test bal --market --exchange C --now 2024/02/01 Expenses
                 C60  Expenses:Test
end test
